{"tid":2036673,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"歲月一身袈裟 終將用愛渡化","createTime":"2020-05-26T15:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T13:54:30.000Z","uid":33777,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be8955ca831f7561be9feacbf53af0c012e09e35","tid":2036673,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>當講「我愛你」變成例行公事</strong><br />\n<br />\n當講「我愛你」變成例行公事<br />\n當每次講完也會問自己真的愛嗎<br />\n當每次輸入「我愛你」也會內疚一次<br />\n我就發現是時候放手<br />\n<br />\n你一直知道<br />\n我一直知道你知道<br />\n大家都裝作不知道<br />\n你是不想<br />\n我是不敢<br />\n<br />\n當感情變成乏味的三個字、敷衍的例行公事。這真的是愛嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8nFypbh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8nFypbh.jpg&h=e4c7d166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同朋友合作出下散文同文字創作<br />\n不定時更新<br />\nIG同步更新<br />\n<br />\nIG:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mind.ful.writing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmind.ful.writing%2F&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=5103c30b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/mind.ful.writing/</a>"},{"pid":"5bebd4bd8a913143dbd8fd73383c41adb3e5ced1","tid":2036673,"uid":358208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"唔會常講，因為太沉重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea53d45155a926db7560027f5ab53ea9aced868","tid":2036673,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:20:49.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"32ac1935a7a2560fdd8fd7bca9c4fffaa3f9cb6d","tid":2036673,"uid":33777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T14:34:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>特等席</strong><br />\n<br />\n夜半無聲<br />\n你從特等席上悄悄退下<br />\n一夜過後<br />\n你已不再把我放在心上<br />\n兩夜過後<br />\n對話欄已消失你的訊息<br />\n那晚過後<br />\n夢境亦漸失去你的影子<br />\n<br />\n雁過留聲<br />\n人過卻只留下無情<br />\n座位再默默地等待新的過客<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DATL7zv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDATL7zv.jpg&h=0b02265a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a08a88cf491f541e057471460103c5ea4e187d10","tid":2036673,"uid":901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f583f06ac1f20c5bb58acfe4cc2f02c9032ee32","tid":2036673,"uid":33777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>奢望</strong><br />\n<br />\n我們還可以當朋友嗎<br />\n大概可以吧<br />\n至少給我留一點希望<br />\n或許有一天<br />\n我們能夠回到最初<br />\n或許有一天<br />\n我們可以回到最初<br />\n<br />\n本以為一子錯<br />\n殊不知你卻告訴我<br />\n或許我們從最初已是錯<br />\n眼裡漸漸模糊的焦距<br />\n望著你毫不猶豫揮袖而去<br />\n心化作飛灰隨風散去<br />\n思念化作泡影隨水漂泊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFigCCk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFigCCk.jpg&h=ecb14233&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf7e202d8b8bc4880c8ab1c3a1d0de3238ab6d7b","tid":2036673,"uid":235414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:03:56.000Z","msg":"幾高質，讀落去有共鳴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecaa02c2b7c78d51a4174ad5f74542728004219","tid":2036673,"uid":33777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:54:30.000Z","msg":"泡影<br />\n<br />\n共你一起登上五光十色的摩天輪<br />\n畏高的你流露出一臉幸福的呆相<br />\n忙著拍下窗外黃昏街頭的我<br />\n突然被你從後輕輕擁抱<br />\n身後溫柔的力量<br />\n輕輕拂過的暖風<br />\n<br />\n與你漫步海灘<br />\n遠遠傳來海鷗歡愉的叫聲<br />\n近近濺起海浪拍打的水花<br />\n泡沫將我慢慢地包圍、碎開<br />\n一切皆化為泡影<br />\n<br />\n沒有永恆不散的光輝<br />\n唯有一刻絢爛的煙火<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQS9k7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQS9k7E.jpg&h=6bf693ae&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}